===Noun===
'''copyright''' (''uncountable and countable. plural:'' [[copyrights]])

#<!--NRightToPublish--> (''uncountable'') The right by law to be the entity which determines who may publish, copy and distribute a piece of writing, music, picture or other work of authorship.
#(''countable'') Such an exclusive right as it pertains to one or more specific works.
#<!--NSymbol©--> (''countable'') The symbol [[©]]. Also called '''copyright symbol'''.

